<body>
  <%= render 'shared/navbar' %>

  <div class="banner">
    <div class="name-role-description">
      <div class="name-role">
        <h2>Agathe Badia</h2>
        <h1 class="title">Junior Developer</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="description-card">
        <p>I am a Junior Developer with a background in tech recruiting. After three years in the HR field and talking with many passionate developers, I decided to become a developer myself!</p>
        <span class="social-media">
          <p>Follow me :)</p>
